\subsubsection{Unescaping newlines}

Canvas CSV exports contain literal [[\textbackslash n]] strings (two characters:
backslash followed by n) rather than actual newline characters. Before we can
properly detect and format code, we must convert these escaped newlines to
actual newline characters.

